# Design System Rules

## Typography
- Headlines: `font-serif` (DM Serif Display)
- Body text: `font-sans` (DM Sans)
- Hero headlines: 64px (text-6xl), line-height 1.08
- Section headlines: 44px (text-4xl)
- Body text: 17px, line-height 1.7

## Colors (CSS Variables)
- `var(--green)` #22c55e - Primary CTAs
- `var(--green-dark)` #16a34a - Hover states
- `var(--dark)` #111111 - Dark sections, secondary buttons
- `var(--cream)` #faf9f7 - Alternating backgrounds
- `var(--text-primary)` #111111
- `var(--text-secondary)` #555555
- `var(--text-muted)` #888888

## Spacing
- Section padding: `py-28 px-14` (110px, 56px)
- Mobile section: `py-16 px-6`
- Card gaps: 32px
- Grid gaps: 48-64px

## Components
- Buttons: rounded-lg (8px), py-3 px-6
- Cards: rounded-2xl (20px)
- Icons: rounded-xl (16px)

## Animations (Framer Motion)
- Default: `whileInView={{ opacity: 1, y: 0 }}`
- Initial: `initial={{ opacity: 0, y: 20 }}`
- Duration: 0.6s
- Viewport: `viewport={{ once: true }}`
- Stagger children by 0.1s

## Never
- Use Inter, Roboto, or system fonts for visible text
- Use Lorem ipsum
- Use stock photo URLs
- Skip mobile responsive styles
